<del rend="strikethrough">b g </del> <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> doch ſo habt </del> doch ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l16">habt Jr Jn ledig gelaſſen / Alſo / daʒ Er euch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> brief </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l17">ſchicken ſülle / daʒ Er <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger ſey / Alſo laſſen vvir euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_206_r1l18">vviſſen / daʒ derſelb peter pecʒel <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger iſt / vnd </ab>
